Revision history for Alien-LibYAML

2.05      2019-04-27 21:08:14 -0400
  - Use https instead of http.
  - Fix for fedora system install (gh#3)
    see rt#129323, and
    https://github.com/Perl5-FFI/FFI-CheckLib/issues/13
  - Use Decode::Mojo plugin instead of Decode::HTML (gh#4)

2.04      2018-06-13 04:23:58 -0400
  - Production release identical to 2.03_01

2.03_01   2018-06-12 08:59:54 -0400
  - Build dynamic libary for FFI for share installs

2.02      2018-06-11 19:17:08 -0400
  - Moved repository to the Perl5-Alien org

2.01      2017-03-22 15:30:53-04:00 America/New_York
  - Specify minimum version of Path::Tiny

2.00      2017-03-22 15:27:48-04:00 America/New_York
  - Migrate to Alien::Build + alienfile

